The Sentencing Project (Feb, 1992). <i>Also see</i> Keri A.
Gould, <i>Turning Rat and Doing Time for Uncharged, Dismissed, Or
Acquitted Crimes: Do the Federal Sentencing Guidelines Promote
Respect for the Law?</i>, 10 <b>N.Y.L.S. Journal of Human Rights</b>
at 1 (1993). </p>

