<title>Indian Hemp Drugs Commission Report - Note by Mr. G. A.
Grierson</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR" content="Microsoft FrontPage 1.1">
<meta name="FORMATTER" content="Microsoft FrontPage 2.0">
