<html>

<head>
<title>Board of Directors of the Drug Abuse Council</title>
<meta name="GENERATOR"
content="Internet Assistant for Microsoft Word 2.0z Beta">
</head>

<body>

<p> </p>
</body>

<body bgcolor="#ffffff">

<p><img src="../../../graphics/blueline.gif"> </p>

<h1>The Facts About Drug Abuse </h1>

<p> <b>The Drug Abuse Council, 1980</b> </p>

<p> <img src="../../../graphics/blueline.gif"> </p>

<p> <font size="5">Board of Directors of the Drug Abuse Council</font>
</p>

<p> Bethuel M. Webster, Chairman </p>

<p> Webster &amp; Sheffield </p>

<p> New York, N.Y. </p>

<p> Daniel X. Freedman, M.D., Vice-Chairman </p>

<p> Professor and Chairman </p>

<p> Department of Psychiatry </p>

<p> University of Chicago </p>

