Thank you for visiting our Web site.  You should be able to find most 
information under "General Information" or under a specific administration's
home page in "Browse The DOT Administrations".<P>

You can use the DOT Web site as a starting point to reach other DOT web sites
and other Federal, State, and International government and transportation 
related sites.<P>

Our server is continually updated, so check in under "Whats New" to see what
new sections we've added since your last visit.<P>

