and how they work.<BR>
</P>

<P><IMG SRC="everyday.jpg" HEIGHT=96 WIDTH=65></P>

<P><B>Everyday Cancer Risks and How to Avoid Them</B><I> Mary Levestein</I>
$11.95 There are many things everyone can do to minimize, if not avoid,
the risk of cancer. But this involves knowing the risks, and what choices
one must make to improve survival odds.</P>

<P><BR>
