<H5>Friday February 14, 1997<BR>18:42:02 EST</H5>

<H4>Welcome to the Center for Democracy and Technology home page!  The 
Center For Democracy and Technology is a non-profit public interest 
organization based in Washington, DC.  CDT's mission is to develop and 
advocate public policies that advance constitutional civil liberties and 
democratic values in new computer and communications technologies.</H4>
</CENTER>

