<li><a href = "http://www.w3.org/pub/WWW/PICS/">PICS</a>, a joint Industry, public interest gorup, and MIT initiative to develop common standards to facilitate user choice and parental control in interactive media. CDT co-chairs the public policy committee.
</ul>
